query:
SELECT g.id, g.nome, COUNT(re.id) as total_exames
FROM gestantes g
INNER JOIN resultadosExames re ON g.id = re.gestanteId
GROUP BY g.id, g.nome
ORDER BY total_exames DESC
LIMIT 5;
